# Sentry · LLM error tracking
# 拿 DSN: https://sentry.io → Settings → Projects → <project> → Client Keys (DSN)
# Auth token: https://sentry.io → Settings → Account → API → Auth Tokens (scopes: project:releases, org:read)
SENTRY_DSN=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=
SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=
SENTRY_ORG=
SENTRY_PROJECT=newshock
